<h2 class="h3">SONA: School of Nursing Assistant</h2>
<p>Robot dogs have emerged in health and patient care settings as innovative tools for providing companionship, reducing stress, and assisting with therapy. SONA integrates aspects of care and monitoring into its interactive capabilities with specialized sensors that can monitor health indicators or remind patients to take their medication.</p>
</main>
